{"tid":2259802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好憎啲人坐交通工具一個人坐兩個位？","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T06:29:22.000Z","uid":19601,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"529b425801d45b58209a05d3b11aee545df2c650","tid":2259802,"uid":19601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n成撚日都係<br />\n隻腳撐都大一大 坐哂兩個位<br />\n好多人怕事寧願唔坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學撚哂大陸人啲野<br />\n冇啲公民意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我啱先就一野坐落去<br />\n專登仲要坐落佢隻腳個位度撞一撞佢<br />\n佢睥撚住我<br />\n我話：咦乜我坐錯位咩？<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大快人心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05aa93630fee1317d4e9e1d857daffd2e0d28cf0","tid":2259802,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/015235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F015235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e1ab1654&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0624cef6475e7e29994cc619b558099e549fcac","tid":2259802,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05aa93630fee1317d4e9e1d857daffd2e0d28cf0","tid":2259802,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/015235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F015235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e1ab1654&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"𠵱一個人坐5個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7ff61c25a7cc551eace177aea24a93d3c77